Invocation Name: work boots
Developer Terms of Use
des:
You can use the Work Boots app to track your recent CAT or Wolverine order or ask questions about work boots.
After the Welcome Message, simply say what you want to learn about, for example:

• I want to learn how to break in my boots
• What is the best way to clean my boots?
• How do I take care of my boots?
• Track my order

Remember to check back regularly to get the latest tips and tricks for your boots!
